mktorrent Version 4.0 modded

added:
"-s,            : start the daemon\n" (Starts a new partial torrent and runs the mktorrent instance in background until torrent gets finalized)
"-x             : do partial hashing\n" (Add files to a partial torrent and hash them)
"-f             : create the final .torrent from the parts\n" (Finalize the torrent after all partial are added)
